thread.title: BRIEF-Wutong Holding Group sees FY 2017 net profit up 19.1 pct to 48.8 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Wutong Holding Group sees FY 2017 net profit up 19.1 pct to 48.8 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - wutong holding group co ltd

text:
Jan 31 (Reuters) - Wutong Holding Group Co Ltd
* Says it sees net profit for FY 2017 to increase by 19.1 percent to 48.8 percent, or to be 200 million yuan to 250 million yuan
* Says the net profit of FY 2016 was 168 million yuan
* Comments that increased income from IT service business as main reason for the forecast
